    <!-- Chosen Palette: "Warm Neutral Harmony" - A calming palette with a light beige/off-white background, complemented by soft grays, a gentle teal for accents, and a dark slate for text. -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The website is structured as a linear, scrolling single-page application, divided into thematic sections: Home, About Us, Services, Why Choose Us, How It Works, Try Our AI, Testimonials, and Contact. A sticky navigation bar at the top provides quick access to these sections, highlighting the user's current position on the page. This linear flow is intuitive for a marketing website, guiding the user through the value proposition step-by-step while allowing them to jump directly to areas of interest like services or contact information. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
        - Hero Section: Features a bold headline, clear call-to-action, and a brief value statement. Goal: Capture attention & Inform. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS.
        - About Us: Presents the company's mission, vision, and the founder's unique blend of skills. Goal: Build trust & Inform. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS.
        - Services: Uses interactive cards with hover effects to reveal more detailed information about each service. This prevents visual clutter while offering depth. Goal: Inform & Engage. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS, JS for interactivity.
        - Why Choose Us: Highlights key differentiators and benefits in an easy-to-digest list format. Goal: Persuade & Inform. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS.
        - How It Works: Visualizes the client engagement process using a clear, step-by-step layout. Goal: Explain & Simplify. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS.
        - Try Our AI: A new interactive section featuring an AI-powered content idea generator. Users input business type and topic to get LLM-generated ideas, demonstrating the "AI for Content & Communication Automation" service directly. Goal: Engage & Demonstrate Value. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS, JS (for user input handling, API call to Gemini, and dynamic content display).
        - Testimonials: A section for future social proof. Goal: Build credibility. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS.
        - Contact Us: Provides clear contact information and a simple form. Goal: Convert leads. Method: HTML, Tailwind CSS.
        - CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used.
    -->
